        <!-- BRIDGE FOOD LLM -->
        <h2>🧠 Bridge Food LLM Integration (Qwen 3.5 Plus)</h2>
        
        <div class="section">
            <h3>Pricing</h3>
            <pre>Input:  $0.11 per 1M tokens
Output: ~$0.66 per 1M tokens

100K users × 52 weeks × 2 recs/week = 10.4M calls/year
TOTAL: ~$2,600/year ✅</pre>

            <h3>System Prompt</h3>
            <p>You are a Sensory Feeding Expert specializing in the SOS Approach. Recommend bridge foods matching the child's sensory profile with parent-friendly explanations (not clinical).</p>

            <h3>Implementation</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>API endpoint: <code>POST /api/bridge-foods/recommend</code></li>
                <li>Input: Child's sensory profile + safe foods + history</li>
                <li>Cache: 24 hours (avoid excessive API calls)</li>
                <li>Fallback: Revert to current algorithm if API fails</li>
                <li>Learning: Track parent feedback → refine future recommendations</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

