                    <td>Reach TASTE on new food</td>
                    <td>+50</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>7-day streak</td>
                    <td>+100</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>30-day streak</td>
                    <td>+500</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>60-day streak</td>
                    <td>+1,000</td>
                </tr>
            </table>

            <h3>Planet Progression (PHASE-based, not food-count)</h3>
            <pre>Planet 1: Unlock first food, progress with 3+ LOOK → 50 pts
Planet 2: Unlock 3+ TOUCH, progress with 5+ → 500 pts
Planet 3: Unlock 3+ SMELL, progress with 5+ → 600 pts
Planet 4: Unlock 3+ LICK, progress with 5+ → 750 pts
Planet 5: Unlock 3+ TASTE, progress with 10+ → 1,000 pts
Planet 6: Unlock 3+ bridge foods, progress 5+ → 1,200 pts
Planet 7: Unlock 5+ food groups, progress all 9 colors → 1,500 pts
Planet 8: Unlock master (50+ foods), complete goal → 2,000 pts</pre>

            <p style="margin-top: 20px;"><strong>See full economy spec at:</strong> <code>POINTS-REWARDS-ECONOMY-BRIEF.md</code></p>
        </div>

